# Environment Variables for Cloudflare Pages

# No public environment variables are needed in .env for production
# The following secrets must be configured in Cloudflare Pages dashboard:
#
# Required Cloudflare Pages Environment Variables:
# - RESEND_API_KEY: Your Resend API key for sending emails
# - RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY: Your Google reCAPTCHA v3 secret key
#
# Note: The reCAPTCHA site key is hardcoded in the Contact component
# (6LeUNBgsAAAAACpEykq296IxdhZPgjl1gNAP1scs)
